The MCU seems ready as ever to start reintroducing some of the characters they've reacquired since the Fox Acquisition. Before we say goodbye to THOSE versions of the characters join us as we pit two PRE-MCU films against one another. Which Was Worse returns with a blast from the past as Ghost Rider (2007) goes one-on-one with Fantastic Four (2005) to decide WHICH WAS WORSE! Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

